    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade 2019 Porsche 718 Cayman that defines the 'mint' standard. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen a drop of rain. The Guards Red exterior is absolutely flawless, featuring a deep, mirror-like shine protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; you will not find a single rock chip, swirl mark, or blemish on any panel. The interior is equally impressive, with the black leather upholstery still retaining its factory matte finish and 'new car' scent. There is zero compression or wear on the seat bolsters, and the dashboard and trim are free from any sun exposure or scratches. Every switch, dial, and electronic feature operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is indistinguishable from new, supported by a comprehensive service portfolio from authorized Porsche centers. It currently sits on a brand-new set of Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. This is an uncompromising example for the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
